{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/colon-colorful-beat-keseharian-grup-idol-jepang-yang-nggak-biasa/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"CoLoN: Colorful Beat – Keseharian Grup Idol Jepang Yang Nggak Biasa","content":"\n<p>Sebelumnya kamu sudah kenalan dengan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/colon-tercera-trapsmois-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"grup idol CoLoN: (opens in a new tab)\">grup idol CoLoN:</a> yang mana dalam acara Ennichisai 2019 lalu memperkenalkan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"komik terbaru mereka (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/colon-japan-ennichisai-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\">komik terbaru mereka</a> di CIAYO Comics. Nah, komik tersebut kini sudah tayang dan memiliki beberapa episode yang sudah bisa kamu baca. Seperti apa kisahnya? Yuk ikuti di komik CoLoN: Colorful Beat!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54645\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/colon-colorful-beat-keseharian-grup-idol-jepang-yang-nggak-biasa/attachment/05-colon-colorful-beat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-colon-colorful-beat\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" alt=\"Keseharian para anggota idol group di CoLoN: Colorful Beat. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54645\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-colon-colorful-beat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/05-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Keseharian para anggota idol group di CoLoN: Colorful Beat. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Komik CoLoN: Colorful Beat bakal mengangkat kisah keseharian anggota\nCoLoN: baik di dalam maupun di luar panggung. Mengusung format komik 4koma,\nkomik ini cocok banget buat dibaca sambil mengisi waktu kosong, seperti di jam\nistirahat atau saat menunggu teman. Cerita utamanya dimulai dari kemunculan dua\nanggota CoLoN: baru yang tiba di asrama mereka. Ternyata, para penghuni asrama\nCoLoN: adalah siluman binatang!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54641\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/colon-colorful-beat-keseharian-grup-idol-jepang-yang-nggak-biasa/attachment/01-colon-colorful-beat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-colon-colorful-beat\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" alt=\"Yogo, Ishibashi, dan Nakanishi. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54641\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-colon-colorful-beat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Yogo, Ishibashi, dan Nakanishi. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ishibashi Takumi dan Nakanishi Yuki merupakan dua member CoLoN: yang\nbaru bergabung. Masing-masing merupakan siluman beruang dan rubah. Ishibashi\nmengaku punya tubuh yang kuat, sementara Nakanishi pandai membuat orang\nbingung. Buktinya adalah ia bisa menghilang saat tidak ada orang yang\nmelihatnya. Bingung kan? Mereka disambut oleh senpai para anggota CoLoN:, yaitu\nYogo Hayato. Sosoknya sangat serius dan tegas, namun kadang sedikit kekanakan\njuga.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54642\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/colon-colorful-beat-keseharian-grup-idol-jepang-yang-nggak-biasa/attachment/02-colon-colorful-beat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-colon-colorful-beat\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" alt=\"Fujinawa, Kurosawa, dan Leoga. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54642\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-colon-colorful-beat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Fujinawa, Kurosawa, dan Leoga. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada lagi Fujinawa Yudai dan Kurosawa Kengo, siluman anjing dan kelinci\nyang sudah berteman sejak lama. Kurosawa sifatnya lebih pemalu daripada\nFujinawa, tapi jangan sampai membuatnya marah. Menurut Fujinawa, kalau\nKengocchi – panggilan akrab Kurosawa – marah, bahkan Fujinawa bisa dibuat\nkewalahan! Lalu ada siluman rusa Leoga yang bisa tidur tanpa menutup matanya.\nKemampuan yang unik ya?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54643\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/colon-colorful-beat-keseharian-grup-idol-jepang-yang-nggak-biasa/attachment/03-colon-colorful-beat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-colon-colorful-beat\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" alt=\"Goto, Satou, dan Kimura. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54643\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-colon-colorful-beat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Goto, Satou, dan Kimura. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kemudian ada siluman serigala Goto Nozomu yang cuek bebek dengan\nsituasi di sekitarnya. Sementara itu siluman harimau Satou Takumi sangat narsis dan hobi\nberdandan. Terakhir adalah siluman musang Kimura Rita yang sangat suka minum\nkopi.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54644\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/colon-colorful-beat-keseharian-grup-idol-jepang-yang-nggak-biasa/attachment/04-colon-colorful-beat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-colon-colorful-beat\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-colon-colorful-beat.jpg\" alt=\"Para anggota CoLoN: siap menyambut tantangan di depan bersama-sama! Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54644\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-colon-colorful-beat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-colon-colorful-beat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Para anggota CoLoN: siap menyambut tantangan di depan bersama-sama! Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Mulai sekarang mereka bersembilan akan tinggal bersama dan tampil sebagai idol group CoLoN:. Seperti apa ya kegiatan mereka setiap harinya, dan apakah sosok siluman mereka akan mengganggu aktivitas sebagai idol? Ikuti di komik CoLoN: Colorful Beat yang diciptakan penulis Snow Rexilium, desainer karakter Dike Akbar, ilustrator Nataeliza, serta colorist Alie Fachri. Baca komiknya setiap hari Kamis pukul 17:00 WIB hanya di CIAYO Comics.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fciayogames%2Fvideos%2F1232656710249205%2F&#038;show_text=0&#038;width=560\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowTransparency=\"true\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Ikuti pula medsos CoLoN: di  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CoLoNbacs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Facebook</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://twitter.com/CoLoN_bacs\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/colon_japan/\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a>, serta <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2pNq3RJy8B4qWRSsS31yPg\" target=\"_blank\">channel Youtube</a>. Setiap member pun punya akun medsos masing-masing yang bisa kamu cek satu per satu <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://colon-japan.com/profile/\" target=\"_blank\">di sini</a>. Nantikan pula visual novel CoLoN: Magical Showtime di aplikasi CIAYO Stories!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e03208ff-d01a-5746-93f0-4ccbf3b8e0b6"}}}